<%= render "shared/header" %>
<div id="content">
  <div class="masthead">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="white text-center">The court system is confusing. Let us clear it up for you.</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 white text-center">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3>The Problem</h3>
              <p class="sans-serif">Municipal court systems, like those found in St. Louis provide poor user experiences and make accessing information difficult for modern societies. Additionally, many Americans do not have access to credit cards, home internet, smart phones or personal transportation adding another level of difficultly to accessing this valuable information that can leading to warrants for failure to appear in court and missed revenue opportunities for local municipalities.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3>The Solution</h3>
              <p class="sans-serif">ClearCourts.org allows anyone to get instant access to their municipal court records using a simple online form and via text-messaging. By creating a free service powered by the same technologies as modern SAAS products sold in the private sector which require excellent user experiences for successful adoption, governments can now give itâ€™s citizens valuable information at their fingertips.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3 col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
          <%= link_to "Give it a Try", new_session_path, id: "get-started", class: "btn btn-primary btn-block btn-md white-border" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div> <!-- .masthead -->

  <%= render "shared/icons" %>

  <div id="banner" class="about">
    <div class="overlay"></div> <!-- .overlay -->
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center">
          <h2 class="gray">Origin Story</h2>
          <p><span class="gray">Clear</span><span class="green">Courts</span> is the result of GlobalHack V which took place September 11-13, 2015 in St. Louis, MO. In it's first civic challenge, GlobalHack presented pain points felt when citizens begin to navigate their legal concerns. 
          </p>
          <p>
            We built a platform that empowering our citizens by giving them instant access anytime anywhere via web and text (SMS).
            Responsive web app that is friendly on both desktop and mobile devices, with the even more accessible SMS automation system.
            By having SMS access to court data, anyone with a phone (even dumb phones) can have access to the courts.
            Low income citizens who use a pre-paid phone without internet access can still use service by integrating Twilio.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div> <!-- #banner -->
</div>